    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/RentalTemplates/RentalOfferTemplateShape.ttl/> (RentalPermissionTemplate-preDutyPropertyShape): In an ids:RentalOffer/-Request within the ids:Permission the ids:preDuty property must point to an ids:Duty with at least one of (ids:assigner or ids:assignee) pointing to a participant, ids:action pointing to ids:Action (1) and the ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint (2). Within the ids:Action (1) the ids:includedIn property must point to idsc:COMPENSATE and the ids:actionRefinement property must point to an ids:Constraint (3). Within the ids:Action (1) the ids:Constraint (3) must have ids:leftOperand pointing to idsc:PAY_AMOUNT, ids:operator pointing to idsc:EQ, ids:rightOperand pointing to a fee as xsd:double, ids:unit pointing to an IRI specifying the currency and zero or one ids:pipEndpoint pointing to a PipUri. Within the ids:Duty within the ids:Constraint (2) the ids:leftOperand must point to idsc:POLICY_EVALUATION_TIME, the ids:operator must point to idsc:AFTER and the ids:rightOperand specifies the duration of usage as xsd:duration."@en ;
